snippet.title: Infestation World Trailer
snippet.description:
Infestation World, a zombie-filled sandbox survival game with a focus on competitive multiplayer modes, will host a sneak peek preview from March 14 - 22 before its closed beta begins on March 28.

Infestation World's outbreak will truly begin when a closed beta runs from March 28 - April 3, followed by an open beta on April 6 and a worldwide launch in Q2 2016.
